<style 
      xmlns="http://purl.org/net/xbiblio/csl"
      class="note"
      version="1.0"><info>
    <id />
    <title />
    <updated>2009-08-10T04:49:00+09:00</updated></info><macro name="author">
    <names variable="author">
      <name name-as-sort-order="first" sort-separator=" "/>
      <substitute>

    </names></macro><macro name="theyear">

      <text value="Ignore me" />

    <sort>
      <key macro="author" names-min="3" names-use-first="1" names-use-last="true"/>
      <key macro="theyear" />
    </sort>
    <layout>
      <group delimiter=" ">
        <names variable="author">
          <name/>
        </names>
        <text variable="title" />
        <date variable="issued" date-parts="year" form="text"/>
      </group>
    </layout></bibliography></style>
